Sabre Corp | Professional Hair Salon Distributor | Just another WordPress site




































 


















About
Sabre Corporation distributes premium beauty brands to salons throughout Australia and New Zealand.
Our Mission is to be Australia and New Zealand’s premiere professional hair salon distributor whose passion, professionalism and experience provide optimal partnerships via strategic planning, resulting in combined success.
With over 30 years in the business, this Australian-owned business leads the way with an extensive Salon Support field team, combined with Salon Education as a priority and top-selling Salon Promotions.


