WARNING: Don’t purchase a stun gun before reading the shocking truth! If you've ever shopped around for stun guns, you've seen plenty of extremely high voltage claims - possibly up to 100 million volts. These astronomical figures sound impressive - but the truth is, when it comes to stun guns, claims like these are not only wildly misleading, but also physically impossible. Get the truth. Watch the video to learn more. 















